Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你该上床睡觉了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's nearly your bedtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我还没说完\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm not finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你可能还没说完 ‎不过葡萄酒供应肯定是完了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You might not be, but the wine supply is definitely over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一切都完了 赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, it's all over, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真的没有完\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's really not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎只是世道变了 ‎仅此而已\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Things just changed, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吸血鬼不喜欢改变\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Vampires aren't big on change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那你之前应该告诉卡米拉的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Someone should have told Carmilla that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你还是误会她了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You still misunderstand her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎拜托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎连你都被她变成的样子吓到了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Even you were horrified by what she turned into.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许是因为她计划的庞大\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The scale of it, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还有可能给我们的生活带来的混乱\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And the chaos it would have introduced into our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.12,0:01:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我还是要说 一切的根源\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I still say that at the root of it all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎都在于吸血鬼的属性\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}was the vampire's virtue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们希望一切都保持原样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We want everything to remain the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.44,0:01:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,保持稳定\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}To remain stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吸血鬼的属性 该死\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The vampire's virtue. Bloody hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一直以来都有这种哲学把戏\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's an act of philosophical acrobatics for the ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你想要变聪明时应该闭嘴\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, shush with your trying to be clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们这些人花了60年时间 ‎横冲直撞\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You people spend 60 years bumping into things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,然后管这叫生活\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and call it a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们得从更长远来考虑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We have to take a longer view.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以我们想要稳定\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So we want stability.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你是说你们曾经很稳定\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you're saying you had that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎的确\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎作为四人组 ‎我和我的姐妹们有力量\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}As a quartet, my sisters and I had strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎维持稳定环境的力量\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The strength to enforce a stable environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎力量可以用来发动战争 确实\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Strength can fight a war, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但也可以用来创建庇护所\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but it can also build a shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你听懂了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are you following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎只是过程中会出现一些状况\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just bumping into things along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎小团体比大团体更稳固 丽诺尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Small shapes are stronger than big ones, Lenore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎卡米拉想要的不仅仅是遮蔽风雨的庇护所\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla wanted more than a weatherproof shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎最终是这样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}In the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不过一切 ‎都源自吸血鬼的属性 你明白吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But it all came from that virtue, do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎力量和权力截然不同\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Strength and power are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你要的是力量\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You wanted strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎卡米拉想要权力\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Carmilla wanted power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎到头来 没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}In the end, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是变成了这样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's what it turned into.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎结果也毁了我的生活\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Which is what ruined my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎权力\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎巨大的 国际的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Big, international,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,非外交 部署权力\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}non-diplomatic, projected power
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是另一回事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎它借给你更多威力\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It lends you more might,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不过却不能当作力量\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but it doesn't have the utilities of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎它会让你彻底失败\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It lays eggs in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎它会变成你必须喂养的寄生虫\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It becomes a parasite you have to feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎权力除了侵蚀 什么也不做\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Power does nothing but eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就像吸血鬼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Like a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就像吸血鬼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Like a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,‎展现出真正的自我...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}having been shown what I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎发现自己一直生活在谎言中\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}having found that I have been living a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎结果我还是坐在笼子里 ‎就像被关起来的危险动物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}here I sit in a cage, like a dangerous animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快乐的杂种 艾萨克国王\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}With King Isaac, the happy bastard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一直密切监视着我的生活\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}keeping a very watchful eye on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我从未见他这么开心过\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've never known him so fucking cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这很匪夷所思\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不过他不会伤害你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But he won't harm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他只是想把我关在笼子里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He's just going to keep me in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不会在笼子里坐以待毙的 赫克托\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I'm not going to sit in a cage, Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎即便是跟你一起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not even with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我为你所经历的一切深感抱歉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm sorry for everything you went through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我很抱歉不能在这里帮你完成...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I'm sorry I can't be here to help you through...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎接下来的任何事情\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}whatever comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不过我拒绝像这样活着\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But I refuse to exist like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想看看你总是提到的太阳\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I want to see what's so special
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.31,0:04:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎到底有多么特别\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}about this sun you keep talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎丽诺尔 别这样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Lenore, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎赫克托 ‎没关系\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hector, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是我想做的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎随你 丽诺尔\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Be free, Lenore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你打算怎么办\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想 我会写本书\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think I'm going to write a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎未来的人们应该知道我们所犯的错误\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The future should know the mistakes we made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎最近 我明白了 ‎比我活得更久的...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And recently, I've been caused to know the value...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那些事物的...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and the beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,价值和美好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}of things that live longer than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就只是这样吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is that all there is to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎赫克托 你真是个傻瓜\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hector, you are a silly man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你觉得我的计划怎么样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So, what do you think about my plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是我的计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你只是觉得这是你的计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You just think it was your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就是我的计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我让你觉得这是你的计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I let you think it was your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我把我的计划告诉了你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I told you my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你只是觉得你告诉我了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You just think you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我很聪明\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm very clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我把我的计划告诉了你 ‎让你觉得\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I told you my plan in a way that would make you think
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你自己的主意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}it was your idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,本来就是我自己的主意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was my bloody idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎承认吧 你被打败了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Admit it. You're outmatched.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我才不是那种人 ‎而且 这都是我的主意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am no such thing, and also it was all my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你就这么去想吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You just go on thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以 你答应了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So you agree, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,‎答应什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Agree to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我的计划\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}My plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们打算留下来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're going to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-‎这下糟了  -‎我是个天才\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- Oh, my God. - I'm a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,屈服吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎暂且不说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Ignoring for a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你比我之前预计的要疯狂得多\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that you are considerably more insane than I have previously estimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你确定这是个好主意吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are you sure it's a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 ‎我不...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I mean, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,习惯与人交往\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}used to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们已经习惯你了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They're used to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以 让他们习惯你吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So just let them be used to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你就会习惯他们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you'll get used to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我觉得 为了试着理解这个逻辑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think I felt part of my brain die
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我的一部分大脑快死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}just trying to follow that logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们是人类 适应了就好了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's human. Just roll with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是人类\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Human, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不完全是人类\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎别以为我没注意到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Don't think I haven't noticed you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你跟孤儿们玩在一起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}playing with the orphaned kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎别以为我不知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And don't think I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们之中有人管你叫"爸爸"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}some of them have been calling you "father."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不想说些什么让他们失望\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I didn't want to disappoint them by saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你很有人性\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Very human of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,‎阿鲁卡多 你真是个奇怪的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You, Alucard, are a very odd person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我觉得我可能会喜欢你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think I might like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎阿鲁卡多 她出现了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Alucard, she's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎温和点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她已经两周没跟任何人说过话了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She hasn't talked to anyone in two weeks now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎赛珐\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sypha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你能腾匹马给我吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Can you spare a horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许吧 拿来干嘛\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Possibly. What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我要去做特雷弗和我原本计划做的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am going to do what Trevor and I originally planned to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎回到我的车队里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Rejoin my caravan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你知道你在这里很受欢迎\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You know you are very welcome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谢谢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不过我也非常肯定自己怀孕了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But I am also very definitely pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我应该跟我的族人在一起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I should be with my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而且我的族人很擅长\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And my people are well practiced
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.58,0:10:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎在需要时给女人应有的支持\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}in giving the support a woman needs when it's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎要是我能得到一匹马就好了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If I could just get a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎恭喜你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎继续\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就像我们到达庄园时\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Say it like the way you said it to Trevor
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你对特雷弗说的那样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}when we arrived at the Hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不该恭喜吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Should I not be congratulating?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"公洗"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我还听过更糟糕的发音呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, I've heard worse impressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他爱我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们有了孩子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We made a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这一切会带来崭新而美好的事物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Something new and wonderful will have come from all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我该走了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你应该留下来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You should stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你的好意我心领了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不过我应该跟更多人在一起\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But I should be around more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不能让你成为我唯一依赖的求助对象\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can't let you be the one person I rely on for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而且孩子应该有一个群体\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and a child should have a community.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果你留下来 ‎就会有的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It will. If you stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不明白\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些人不用回德内什蒂\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}These people aren't going back to Danesti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们要围绕着城堡和庄园\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're going to found a new village here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,建一个新的村子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}around the castle and the Hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这个地方有资源\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This place has resources
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是我在德内什蒂给不了我的人民的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I could never give my people in Danesti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们可以改变这里的一切\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We could change everything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们会有学校\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're going to have schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎其中一个学校将是关于\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}one of which will be all about the libraries
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎城堡和庄园的图书馆\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}of the castle and the Hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我希望你能帮我教教\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I was hoping you could help me teach
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这个才华横溢却相当没用的男人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}this brilliant but actually fairly useless man
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如何生活\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}how to live his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不要抱太大的希望\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Don't set your hopes too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎赛珐 ‎我们有真正的机会\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sypha, we have a real chance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让我们的孩子比我们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to make life better for our children
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎生活得更好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}than it was for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这一次 还能更好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}For once, it could be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对我们所有的孩子来说都是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}For all our children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎她真会说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}She's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你有大麻烦了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're in real trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们打算把这个村子叫什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What are you going to call the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎新德内什蒂吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}New Danesti?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想我们可以取名为贝尔蒙特\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I thought we might call it Belmont.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这应该会让所有人都感到困惑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That should confuse everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想我会很乐意住在 ‎一个叫贝尔蒙特的地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think I'd like to live in a place called Belmont.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而且 ‎天啦\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Also, my God,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人的组织能力太差\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}these people are bad at organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们真的打算一整天都从河里‎来来回回\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And are you really going to walk buckets back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,运送水桶吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}from the river all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我还以为你懂科学呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I thought you were a man of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那边的小路也需要拓宽\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The lane's going to need widening over there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那是谁的马\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Whose horse is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎什么马\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎沿小路走着的那匹\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Walking down the lane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎把你的马拴起来 阿鲁卡多\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Tie your horses up, Alucard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果你要建个村子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}If you're founding a village,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就需要把这些东西都整理好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}you need to sort these things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我认识那匹马\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know that horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不过...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎马上有人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}someone's on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊 亲爱的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hello, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,所有问题\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All the questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你赶紧回答\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You answer now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我能想到的就是 ‎圣日耳曼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All I can think of is that Saint Germain
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在死之前打开了无限回廊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}opened the Infinite Corridor just before he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我把匕首插进了死神的身体\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I got the dagger into Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他像太阳一样发起光来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He lit up like the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不一会儿 我就到了回廊里面\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}A second later I was inside the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎接下来当我意识到时 ‎已经脸朝下\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Next thing I knew, I was lying on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,躺在多瑙河北岸了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}by the north bank of the Danube.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真是没想到啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, I'll be damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们这里需要帮助 马上\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We need some help over here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我会没事的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我只是需要睡上一年 换个新的躯体\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I just need about a year's sleep and a new body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那你呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一切都好吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我很好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那就好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你知道最让我害怕的是什么吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You know what scared me the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你最终可能会给孩子起名叫特雷弗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That you might end up calling the kid Trefor after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.99,0:15:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你怎么知道的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}How did you even know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎拜托 ‎是我啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Please. This is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你觉得我是如何做到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}How do you think I've managed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一直单身并且了无牵挂的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to stay single and carefree all these years?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谁能过来杀了这个男人吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Can someone please come over here and kill this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在杀我应该很容易\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It won't be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你真是个粗鲁的白痴 ‎特雷弗·贝尔蒙特\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You are a rude idiot, Trevor Belmont.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎可我爱你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这我也知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我说了 这个男人需要帮助\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I said this man needs help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你好 贝尔蒙特\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hello, Belmont.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那把匕首是怎么回事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Now what was that trick with the dagger?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你好 阿鲁卡多\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Hello, Alucard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎士兵们在塔哥维斯特的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, there were fighters in Targoviste
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,藏身之处\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}hiding in what turned out to be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎原来是王家的宝藏库\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}the royal family's treasure vault,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们只是把东西从那里拿出来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and they were just taking things out of there
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,并且当成护身符\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}as good-luck charms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我开始注意到一些东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I started noticing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎最后收集到了‎一位疯狂的巫师铁匠\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Ended up collecting the pieces of something
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎曾经制造过的物件碎片\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}a mad wizard blacksmith once made to enact
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一件用来跟上帝订立单方面的谋杀自杀契约的物件\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}a very one-sided murder-suicide pact with God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以 ‎你很清楚当你使用这东西时 ‎对你来说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So you knew the thing was probably lethal to you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:16:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是致命的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}when you used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不过我也没有选择的余地\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But didn't see much of a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些人在这里做什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What are all these people doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎欢迎来到我的村子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Welcome to my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你现在有个村子了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You have a village now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎它叫什么名字\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's it called?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎小特雷弗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Treffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎谁能过来杀了我吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Can someone please come over here and kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你看起来怪开心的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You look weirdly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我确实怪开心的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I weirdly am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这真是一段奇特的旅程\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's been a strange ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我很高兴一切都结束了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm happy it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎有趣的是 我生平第一次\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The funny thing is, for the first time in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎完全不知道接下来会发生什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have absolutely no idea what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我只是有一种一切都会值得的感觉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I just have this feeling that it's going to be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就是这样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That's exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.26,0:17:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我怪开心的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm weirdly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.39,0:18:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你还好吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想我们终于赢了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think we finally won.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,丽莎·特佩斯和弗拉德·特佩斯\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Lisa and Vlad Tepes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你得习惯叫自己弗拉德\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You need to get used to calling yourself Vlad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想是这样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不能把你介绍为\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I can't be introducing you as
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"德古拉·特佩斯 老实说 没关系\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}"Dracula Tepes, honestly no relation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,别凑近看他的牙"\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}don't look too closely at his teeth."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你想跟我说的就是这个吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Is this what you really want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你不在那里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后你也死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后你来找我了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you came to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎当然了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Of course I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定会来找你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I could do nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我以为你还有别的选择\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I assumed you had other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎对着撒旦大喊大叫 直到他承认\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Shouting at Satan until he admitted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他只是在给你暖椅子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}he was just keeping the chair warm for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那一类的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.69,0:21:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我死去的那一刻\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The second after I died
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎可能是你死后我第一次清醒的时刻\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}might have been the first sane moment I had since you died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你看起来确实非常平静\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You do seem remarkably calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎而你看起来好像有点生气\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you seem a little angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为这些都没有任何意义\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because none of this makes any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你对发生的事情有什么理论吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you have a theory about what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你怎么会认为我有理论\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What makes you think I have a theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你是男人 男人总是有理论\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're a man. Men always have theories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我只知道 我们昨天在田野中醒来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}All I know is that we woke up in a field yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:21:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还偷了一些衣服 ‎我对此还是觉得过意不去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And had to steal some clothes. I still feel bad about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:21:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,今天下午\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You didn't feel bad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你偷那个工头钱包时 却没有觉得过意不去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}about picking that headman's pocket this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他就是头猪\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, he was a pig.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不过我们应该为那些\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But we should do something
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,被我们拿走了衣服的人做点什么 明天吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}for the people we took these clothes from tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们会的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不过在那之后...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们不能回到城堡了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We can't return to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们可怜的孩子 ‎应该给他的生活做个了结\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Our poor boy deserves some closure in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.65,0:22:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许会在未来的某一天\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Perhaps, one day in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但还不是时候\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我有个想法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是理论吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not a theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.40,0:22:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是理论 只是想法\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not a theory. Just a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.65,0:22:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我觉得我们应该去旅行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think we should travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎去哪里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在想英国\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was thinking about England.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎东北海岸有个地方\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's a place on the northeast coast
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那里应该很美\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that is supposed to be beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.48,0:22:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们说 那里几乎没有阳光\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And they say the sun barely shines there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是叫怀特比还是惠特比之类的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}White-by, or Whitby, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我猜那里偏远又孤独\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Remote and lonely, I presume?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一座修道院 有男有女\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}An abbey. Men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎据说还有大约20栋房子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And about 20 houses, I've read.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.56,0:23:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还有海景 和鱼\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sea views. Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎鱼吗 那我怎么能拒绝\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Fish. How can I resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没有你 我是不会好起来的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm not going to get better without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没有你 我也绝对不会好起来的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I was never going to be better without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.24,0:23:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们有了第二次机会\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We have a second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还有一个崭新的未来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And a brand-new future.
